{"tid":977062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人今鋪撐林鄭","createTime":"2019-01-11T01:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T02:18:02.000Z","uid":32638,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e729d5aa4672a52db60589e79e8e9b2e2b17aca","tid":977062,"uid":32638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"今鋪cut 廢老金 無可否認 林鄭講野係好涼薄<br />\n<br />\n話自己60歲都仲做十幾個鐘既呢d廢話<br />\n<br />\n但係的而且確 佢係個預算案到 白紙黑字寫到明<br />\n<br />\n依家個個議員屌鳩佢唔講 話佢老屈<br />\n<br />\n屌你班垃圾議員 即係冇撚睇過份野啦仆街<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對事唔對人 今鋪我覺得林鄭冇錯 係涼薄姐<br />\n<br />\n佢針對人口政策 個退休年齡 去到六十五歲<br />\n<br />\n改變個福利 令人做耐d野 好合理 你班議員個時又話得<br />\n<br />\n依家個個出黎屌政府 班議員就將個波推比林鄭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理性討論 獨立睇呢件事 唔好拉埋其他野黎講"},{"pid":"f94bb879daf3f8d73fa24af8bb423a1607b2944d","tid":977062,"uid":32638,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"利申番先 等陣比人屌五毛<br />\n<br />\n政府都係on99架啦"},{"pid":"17365d48a3c5f39f6410b28764ac241f06e831bd","tid":977062,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7cc823e3ac2e409bd8b893257691806196a4822","tid":977062,"uid":32638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17365d48a3c5f39f6410b28764ac241f06e831bd","tid":977062,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"150人唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n150隻垃圾就好有問題"}]}